channel.title: I added items to shop, now I can't log in.. Someone help!
channel.description:
I added some barrows items in-place of capes in a ship in pimpscape source on my server. But, now when I try to log in, it just stays at a black screen. I dont know how to post pics honestly, so I can't tell ya much. Can someone send me their shops.cfg file please? It would be of great help. :)
OMG, I help people day after day... And then when I post, I can't get a single reply.
